13-10-2025 (Monday)
                Introduction class,
                The first class was conducted to introduce the project. The mentor explained the goals, steps, and what we’ll be doing throughout the project.
14-10-2025 (Tuesday)
                Project documents shared,
                All project-related documents were shared, including the link to download the dataset and other reference files.
15-10-2025 (Wednesday)
                Dataset downloaded,
                The dataset was downloaded successfully and checked for completeness.
16-10-2025 (Thursday)
                No class,
                There were no scheduled sessions.
17-10-2025 (Friday)
                Dataset preprocessing started,
                Began analysing the dataset.
18th Oct (saturday)
                Applied Otsu’s Thresholding and morphological filters (dilation, erosion) to generate a clean binary defect 
                mask for initial defect detection.
22nd Oct (Tuesday)
                Used OpenCV contour detection to outline each defect in the binary mask.
23rd Oct (Wednesday)  
                Implemented bounding box extraction to crop and save Regions of Interest (ROIs) for each detected defect.
